imdb.plot outline: A heist comedy unlike any other, "Robin Banks" is a raucous send-up of classic heist movies, starring a trio of bumbling bank robbers: Bobby, the loose cannon (Cavalero); Robert, the tech whiz (Zuckerman); and Robin (Mosely), the leader, who tries (and fails) to keep the group from screwing up. Whether they're hitting on the hostages, turtle-heading during a big robbery, or hiring a sushi chef to feed everyone in the bank, "Robin Banks" turns every tense theft trope on its ear, proving there's no handbook for crime...and if there were, Robin would probably shoot it for knowing too much.
